Barrymore's shot, one of Alba's, he started to scream "Crazy-bot 
(Virgo) and Crazy bot's friend can't hurt Termitron" and he fired 5 
times against MCGowan, 5 times against Stiller, 5 times against Alba 
and 10 times against Virgo. 

Nightlight stood up and looked to Depp and answered "I'm Nightlight"; 
she quickly moved in order to avoid Virgo's darts. She looked Virgo 
shooting at Trinity "TRINITY LOOK OUT!!!!!" 

Trinity jumped and avoided Virgo's yellow dart, but red dart hits 
her "YOU shoot me!!!"said anger TRinity"I don't like that People
